<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', {
        title: '登录 - 负载均衡测试站点',
        extraCss: '<style>.login-container { max-width: 480px; margin: 30px auto; } .session-info { background-color: var(--color-bg-card); padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: var(--radius-input); margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-text-strong); } .login-container .btn { width: 100%; padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; justify-content: center; }</style>'
    }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav', { active: 'home', serverIP: serverIP }) %>

    <div class="container login-container">
        <h1>
            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'log-in', size: 22 }) %>
            登录测试
        </h1>

        <div class="session-info">
            <strong>当前会话ID:</strong> <%= sessionId %>
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-info">
            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'shield', size: 14 }) %>
            <div>
                <strong>测试说明</strong> 登录后将创建会话，用于测试负载均衡器的会话保持功能。可以使用任意用户名和密码进行测试。
            </div>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
            <div class="status status--error">
                <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'x', size: 14 }) %>
                <%= error %>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="POST" action="/login">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="username">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'user', size: 13 }) %>
                    用户名
                </label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required placeholder="输入任意用户名" autocomplete="username">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="password">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'key', size: 13 }) %>
                    密码
                </label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required placeholder="输入任意密码" autocomplete="current-password">
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'check', size: 14 }) %>
                登录
            </button>
        </form>

        <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">
            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'home', size: 14 }) %>
            返回主页
        </a>

        <div class="help-block">
            <strong>会话保持测试流程</strong>
            <ol>
                <li>输入任意用户名和密码进行登录</li>
                <li>登录成功后会创建会话并跳转到测试页面</li>
                <li>测试页面会显示会话保持的详细信息</li>
                <li>可多次刷新页面观察会话是否保持</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
